text: Þis sint þa land gemæro þa X hida to Cnugel.
In þæs cumbes heafde to þas cingis gemære west ofer þone cnol to þæn seoh tore to þru broce of þruce on wulfa broc.
Þanon on nunnena dene on þes hlinces heafod.
Þær of dune andlanges shlades up andlang dene up to gosa beorge & so to eadan dic.
Andlang eadan dic to þas cumbes heafode.
